Game ........: Spec Ops 2 - Omega Squad 
Date .....: 2003.11.19 
Video ....: PAL

Ripped: Nothing.

The Spec Ops series comes to the console market. In this episode, players assume the role of a soldier in the Green Berets, the fiercest military unit ever created. Armed and ready to go, the player is then faced with over thirty dangerous recon missions. With both 1st- and 3rd-person point of views, players are sure to be blown away by the never- before- seen visuals unique to this title.

Spec Ops 2: Omega Squad is the first and only 3D real-time tactical Sim for Dreamcast console System, and is a powerful sequel that elevates the Spec Ops series to new levels of white-knuckle combat intensity. 